## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="b2008-151">この実装の<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>呼び出す必要のあるアプリケーションで役に立ちます、`Fill`メソッドの 2 つ以上<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>オブジェクト。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2008-151">This implementation of the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> can be useful in an application that must call the `Fill` method for two or more <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> objects.</span></span>  
  
   
  
