## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="b2008-161">ときに、<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A>プロパティが割り当てられている、以前に作成した<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>、<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>は複製されません。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2008-161">When the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> property is assigned to a previously created <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>, the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> is not cloned.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2008-162">代わりに、 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> 、以前に作成したへの参照を保持<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2008-162">Instead, the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> maintains a reference to the previously created <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="b2008-163">更新操作中に場合<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A>セットと主キーでない情報が存在する、 <xref:System.Data.DataSet>、使用することができます、<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder>自動的に生成するクラス、 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A>、および、を調整するために必要なその他のコマンド<xref:System.Data.DataSet>データベースにします。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2008-163">During an update operation, if <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> is not set and primary key information is present in the <xref:System.Data.DataSet>, you can use the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder> class to automatically generate the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A>, and additional commands needed to reconcile the <xref:System.Data.DataSet> to the database.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2008-164">これを行うには、設定、<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A>のプロパティ、<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2008-164">To do this, set the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> property of the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2008-165">生成ロジックに含まれるキー列の情報も必要です、<xref:System.Data.DataSet>します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2008-165">The generation logic also requires key column information to be present in the <xref:System.Data.DataSet>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2008-166">詳細については、次を参照してください。 [Commandbuilder でのコマンドの生成](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/generating-commands-with-commandbuilders.md)します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2008-166">For more information see [Generating Commands with CommandBuilders](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/generating-commands-with-commandbuilders.md).</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="b2008-167">次の例では、作成、<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>設定と、<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A>と<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A>プロパティ。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2008-167">The following example creates an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> and sets the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> and <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> properties.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2008-168">既に作成するいると想定して、<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleConnection>オブジェクト。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2008-168">It assumes you have already created an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleConnection> object.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Public Shared Function CreateCustomerAdapter(conn As OracleConnection) As OracleDataAdapter   
  
  Dim da As OracleDataAdapter = New OracleDataAdapter()  
  Dim cmd As OracleCommand  
  Dim parm As OracleParameter  
  
  ' Create the SelectCommand.  
  
  cmd = New OracleCommand("SELECT * FROM Dept " & _  
                       "WHERE DName = :pDName AND Loc = :pLoc", conn)  
  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14)  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pLoc", OracleType.NVarChar, 13)  
  
  da.SelectCommand = cmd  
  
  ' Create the DeleteCommand.  
  
  cmd = New OracleCommand("DELETE FROM Dept WHERE DeptNo = :pDeptNo", conn)  
  
  parm = cmd.Parameters.Add("pDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo")  
  parm.SourceVersion = DataRowVersion.Original  
  
  da.DeleteCommand = cmd  
  
  Return da  
End Function  
```  
  
```csharp  
public static OracleDataAdapter CreateCustomerAdapter(OracleConnection conn)  
{  
  OracleDataAdapter da = new OracleDataAdapter();  
  OracleCommand cmd;  
  OracleParameter parm;  
  
  // Create the SelectCommand.  
  
  cmd = new OracleCommand("SELECT * FROM Dept " +  
                       "WHERE DName = :pDName AND Loc = :pLoc", conn);  
  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14);  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pLoc", OracleType.NVarChar, 13);  
  
  da.SelectCommand = cmd;  
  
  // Create the DeleteCommand.  
  
  cmd = new OracleCommand("DELETE FROM Dept WHERE DeptNo = :pDeptNo", conn);  
  
  parm = cmd.Parameters.Add("pDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo");  
  parm.SourceVersion = DataRowVersion.Original;  
  
  da.DeleteCommand = cmd;  
  
  return da;  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="b2008-172">ときに、<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A>プロパティが割り当てられている、以前に作成した<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>オブジェクト、<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>は複製されません。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2008-172">When the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> property is assigned to a previously created <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> object, the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> is not cloned.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2008-173">代わりに、 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> 、以前に作成したへの参照を保持<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2008-173">Instead, <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> maintains a reference to the previously created <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="b2008-174">更新操作中に場合<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A>セットと主キーでない情報が存在する、 <xref:System.Data.DataSet>、使用することができます、<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder>クラスで自動的に生成する<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A>、および調整するために必要なその他のコマンド、 <xref:System.Data.DataSet>データベース。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2008-174">During an update operation, if <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> is not set and primary key information is present in the <xref:System.Data.DataSet>, you can use the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder> class to automatically generate <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A>, and additional commands needed to reconcile the <xref:System.Data.DataSet> to the database.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2008-175">これを行うには、設定、<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A>のプロパティ、<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2008-175">To do this, set the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> property of the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2008-176">生成ロジックに含まれるキー列の情報も必要です、<xref:System.Data.DataSet>します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2008-176">The generation logic also requires key column information to be present in the <xref:System.Data.DataSet>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2008-177">詳細については、次を参照してください。 [Commandbuilder でのコマンドの生成](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/generating-commands-with-commandbuilders.md)します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2008-177">For more information see [Generating Commands with CommandBuilders](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/generating-commands-with-commandbuilders.md).</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="b2008-178">これらの行に追加できる場合、このコマンドの実行には、行が返されます、<xref:System.Data.DataSet>を設定する方法に応じて、<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand.UpdatedRowSource%2A>のプロパティ、<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>オブジェクト。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2008-178">If execution of this command returns rows, these rows may be added to the <xref:System.Data.DataSet> depending upon how you set the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand.UpdatedRowSource%2A> property of the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> object.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="b2008-179">列を更新すると、`LONG RAW`データ型の値を入力するときに例外がスローされます`NULL`列。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2008-179">When you update a column with the `LONG RAW` data type, an exception is thrown when you enter a value of `NULL` in the column.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2008-180">Oracle`LONG RAW`データ型は、Oracle バージョン 8.0 では非推奨の型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2008-180">The Oracle `LONG RAW` data type is a deprecated type in Oracle version 8.0.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2008-181">このエラーを回避するには、使用、`BLOB`データ型の代わりに`LONG RAW`します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2008-181">To avoid this error, use the `BLOB` data type instead of `LONG RAW`.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="b2008-182">次の例では、作成、<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>設定と、<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A>と<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A>プロパティ。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2008-182">The following example creates an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> and sets the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> and <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> properties.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2008-183">既に作成するいると想定して、<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleConnection>オブジェクト。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2008-183">It assumes you have already created an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleConnection> object.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Public Shared Function CreateCustomerAdapter(conn As OracleConnection) As OracleDataAdapter   
  
  Dim da As OracleDataAdapter = New OracleDataAdapter()  
  Dim cmd As OracleCommand  
  
  ' Create the SelectCommand.  
  
  cmd = New OracleCommand("SELECT * FROM Dept " & _  
                       "WHERE DName = :pDName AND Loc = :pLoc", conn)  
  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14)  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pLoc", OracleType.NVarChar, 13)  
  
  da.SelectCommand = cmd  
  
  ' Create the InsertCommand.  
  
  cmd = New OracleCommand("INSERT INTO Dept (DeptNo, DName) " & _  
                       "VALUES (:pDeptNo, :pDName)", conn)  
  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo")  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14, "DName")  
  
  da.InsertCommand = cmd  
  
  Return da  
End Function  
